'''''Razorshark''''' was a [[Wyndham Systems]] [[Starfighter/Legends|small fighter]] owned and operated by [[Egot Pai-4-Yem]]. The ships could usually be found in its hangar in the back of Egot's warehouse, and was once used as an escape craft when the local police forces of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Harridan (planet)|Harridan]] raided the warehouse. He soon took the ''Razorshark'' to the small moon of Harridan where he hid, waiting for the group of [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebels]] who had accidentally led the police to his warehouse. After he saw them leaving the [[Titan (Victory-class)|''Titan'']], Egot commenced fire on the rebel ship. Though he had no real hope of defeating the rebel ship, he had been driven nearly mad with anger. While he was performing this attack, the ''Titan'' came to stop him and captured the ''Razorshark'' in its [[Tractor beam/Legends|tractor beam]], allowing the rebel ship to jump to [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]].

